commit.message:
toplev.c (documented_lang_options): Correct spelling error.

	* toplev.c (documented_lang_options): Correct spelling error.
	(decode_d_option, decode_f_option, main): Likewise.

	* toplev.c (print_time): Avoid SIGFPE when all_time is zero.

From-SVN: r32181

+	(decode_d_option, decode_f_option, main): Likewise.
